{"tid":2245202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：再三強調香港絕無走資情況 稱提早取強姦金違背初心","createTime":"2020-10-16T04:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T05:57:32.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c9fb4833d3f8b7a77953f8728cc0dd64e31e494c","tid":2245202,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"許正宇：本港無出現走資　整體財政狀況仍穩健 <br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇表示，本港無出現走資，政府投入本地生產總值一成作抗疫措施後，財政儲備仍有8000多億，等於約一年的開支，認為整體財政狀況仍穩健，長遠仍對香港有信心。不過他指，過去四個月與去年同期相比，收入大跌兩成，但支出增加七成，因此要小心謹慎，不可以放鬆或鬆懈，要「睇餸食飯」。 <br />\n<br />\n許正宇接受民建聯議員葛珮帆訪問時指，本港金融發展不錯，資產價格未有太幅回落，整個金融市場韌性很強，今年股市每天平均交易量較去年增長約四成，反映香港仍是一個聚財地方，體現投資者對香港的信心。被問到市民可否取回強積金供款應急，許正宇指強積金原意是作退休安排，如果僱員取回供款，退休後就無保障，強調政府三輪防疫抗疫基金已考慮市民需求。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2361874&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=2ba19760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361874</a>"},{"pid":"448b4c83f48acb657abc586bf2c2839e31e19062","tid":2245202,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T04:50:51.000Z","msg":"中共要聽反話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7872fbad9b11c655a10ffe1e771f9d97e8c094","tid":2245202,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVCp0nF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVCp0nF.png&h=f205dd8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f72d71621892f2b5011395605204d08e6e283fb","tid":2245202,"uid":93588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"日日都走緊資啦，唔係洗鬼叫天文台亂掛8號停市拖時間咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7153b0b9249ae3fd6d217804a068b69dc191c68","tid":2245202,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"我拎返的啲錢關你撚事"},{"pid":"6aa3afea65f0df02ed7e0d655c3d9e311b52aabd","tid":2245202,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:52:02.000Z","msg":"即係有啦"},{"pid":"f3055719fc08d62b2c928fa7301efd85b8377150","tid":2245202,"uid":301912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"你有你講，我做我嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f954a653fe81a21f75357eb6b3b580a4369b37df","tid":2245202,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"近排咁多人移民拎MPF 你話冇咪冇囉"},{"pid":"1bac49c881bed2e98c276fcc6e85a6166ece1419","tid":2245202,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">如果僱員取回供款，退休後就無保障</span></span> 係, 我依家堅撐全民退保, 橫撚掂你班仆街都會攞晒d錢填海!"}]}